content: I commute to work 5 days a week, and I take a one-way trip to work in the morning. The cost of a single ticket is $5. I'm not sure about the monthly pass cost, but I can check the website to find out. By the way, I've been taking the 7:15 AM train, which is consistently crowded, except for last Wednesday when there was some issue with the signaling system and the train was delayed by 20 minutes.
